Conformed Copy - L3080 - Private Sector
            Development Loan - Loan Agreement

display_title.display_title:
Conformed Copy - L3080 - Private
            Sector Development Loan - Loan Agreement

5078764.admreg: East Asia and Pacific,East Asia and Pacific

abstracts.cdata!:
The objectives of the Private Sector
            Development Loan Project are to develop the private sector
            by: (i) supporting the substantial policy measures
            undertaken by the Government of Indonesia (GOI), and
            ensuring that they are implemented well; (ii) assisting GOI
            to bring about an early recovery in economic activity,
            consistent with external and internal financial stability;
            and (iii) maintaining the policy dialogue on further reforms
            to promote the efficiency and longer-term viability of the
            economy. The loan will be used to finance general imports of
            goods to meet part of Indonesia's near-term foreign
            exchange requirements, and play a catalytic role in
            mobilizing fast disbursing assistance from other donors.
